title: Cambridge - English In Use Complete Collection [Books & CD-R
description:
Cambridge - English In Use Complete Collection [Books & CD-ROMs]
 <a href="
http://i.imgur.com/CCKQW.jpg" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://i.imgur.com/CCKQW.jpg</a>

Trusted by over 30 million learners the world over, in Use offers the biggest and best range of support for learning English.
With more than 40 titles, covering grammar, vocabulary and pronunciation as well as Professional English, their clear explanations and straightforward practice have made the books a firm favourite with students and teachers alike.

Info: www.cambridge.org/elt/inuse 

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. To Run most of CD-ROM's you will need lastest Daemon Tools Lite with SPTD http://www.daemon-tools.cc/eng/products/dtLite
2. It's important that you create and mount all .ISO and .MDF files through SCSI Virtual Drive! HOW TO:
3. Go to Daemon Tools Preferences > Advanced tab and enable emulation option "SecuROM" Tick IT!
4. All .MDF .MDS and .ISO files tested and works simply just with Daemon Tools Lite 4.45.4(with SPTD ver.1.81) mounted on SCSI Virtual drive and SecuROM emulation option enabled. 
EXCEPT ONE "English Vocabulary in Use Pre-intermediate & Intermediate [2nd Ed] (2006).mds"
To run this you need Y.A.S.U v1.6.9040 + DAEMON Tools Lite v4.30.3 (its old version... and Im not sure its compatibile with Win7...)
- Mount the image files (mdf) using DAEMON Tools Lite v4.30.3
- Install the Vocabulary CD-ROMs
- Place YASU.exe in Daemon Tools folder and run it --> click on 'Cloak' button (for the first time only)
More Information about YASU :http://forum.daemon-tools.cc/f40/
DAEMON Tools Lite v4.30.3 lay down here, try: http://www.filehippo.com/download_daemon_tools/5054/
Y.A.S.U v1.6.9040: http://cdmediaworld.com/cgi-bin/dl.cgi?f=YASU_1.6_9040!zip
If some one know better solution for problem #4, please share it in comments.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
